{
  "id": "adv_event_2303_01_05",
  "title": "ぱじゃパ！\n結成",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "speakerNameEn": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――翌日",
      "translations": {
        "en": "――The next day",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 0,
      "endTime": 1,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2303_01_05/sud_vo_adv_event_2303_01_05-suz001.m4a",
      "text": "……新ユニット、そんなので本当にいいんですの？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…Is it really okay with just that for a new unit?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 1.8999999086,
      "endTime": 6.0879593889,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2303_01_05/sud_vo_adv_event_2303_01_05-chs001.m4a",
      "text": "どう思う？　雫ちゃん",
      "translations": {
        "en": "What do you think? Shizuku-chan",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 6.2879594127,
      "endTime": 8.4879593889,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2303_01_05/sud_vo_adv_event_2303_01_05-szk001.m4a",
      "text": "分からない……私にも……理解、不能……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I don't know… Even I… can't understand it…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 8.6879594127,
      "endTime": 13.484921006299999,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2303_01_05/sud_vo_adv_event_2303_01_05-smr001.m4a",
      "text": "きっと、さとみさんに考えがあるはずだよ\nまずは説明を聞いてみよう？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Surely‚ Satomi-san must have a reason.\nLet's listen to the explanation first‚ okay?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 13.6849210301,
      "endTime": 19.184920839399997,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "stm",
      "speakerName": "橋本さとみ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Satomi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-satomi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2303_01_05/sud_vo_adv_event_2303_01_05-stm001.m4a",
      "text": "お任せ下さい！　では改めて最初からご説明します\n奥山さん、成宮さん、赤崎さん、兵藤さん、白石さん",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Leave it to me! Let me explain from the beginning again.\nOkuyama-san‚ Narumiya-san‚ Akazaki-san‚ Hyodo-san‚ Shiraishi-san",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 19.3849210301,
      "endTime": 30.4666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "stm",
      "speakerName": "橋本さとみ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Satomi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-satomi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2303_01_05/sud_vo_adv_event_2303_01_05-stm002.m4a",
      "text": "新しいユニットのメンバーは、この五人です！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "The members of the new unit are these five people!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 30.6343784133,
      "endTime": 34.647396592199996,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kokoro",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2303_01_05/sud_vo_adv_event_2303_01_05-kkr001.m4a",
      "text": "そこですよ～。合宿に参加したメンバー五人で\nユニットを結成って……安直過ぎじゃないですか～？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Excuse me~. Forming a unit with the five members\nwho participated in the training camp… isn't it too simple~?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 34.847396616,
      "endTime": 43.3965096987,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "stm",
      "speakerName": "橋本さとみ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Satomi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-satomi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2303_01_05/sud_vo_adv_event_2303_01_05-stm003.m4a",
      "text": "いえ。昨夜の枕投げを見て、ぴんと来たんです\nこの五人がいいんだ！　って",
      "translations": {
        "en": "No. After seeing last night's pillow fight‚ it clicked for me.\nThese five are it!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 43.5965097226,
      "endTime": 50.2386861598,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kokoro",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2303_01_05/sud_vo_adv_event_2303_01_05-kkr002.m4a",
      "text": "枕をぶつけられておいて、よくそんな風に思えますね～\nある意味、尊敬します～",
      "translations": {
        "en": "To think you'd feel that way after getting hit with a pillow~\nIn a sense‚ I respect you~",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 50.4386861837,
      "endTime": 57.118541469,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "stm",
      "speakerName": "橋本さとみ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Satomi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-satomi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2303_01_05/sud_vo_adv_event_2303_01_05-stm004.m4a",
      "text": "決め手は……みなさんの「素」の可愛さです！\n驚きました。みんなそのままでも凄く可愛いんですから",
      "translations": {
        "en": "The deciding factor is… your \"natural\" cuteness!\nI was surprised. You're all incredibly cute as you are.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 57.3573473249,
      "endTime": 67.88612254,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2303_01_05/sud_vo_adv_event_2303_01_05-suz002.m4a",
      "text": "ふ、ふ～ん？　私達がいついかなる時でも可愛いのは\n確かに真実ですけど",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Hm? It's true that we're always cute‚\nno matter the circumstances…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 68.0861233268,
      "endTime": 75.6049896751,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kokoro",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2303_01_05/sud_vo_adv_event_2303_01_05-kkr003.m4a",
      "text": "私の方が上ですけどもね～",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I'm still cuter though~",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 75.8049896989,
      "endTime": 78.7233571324,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2303_01_05/sud_vo_adv_event_2303_01_05-smr002.m4a",
      "text": "もう、二人ともちゃんと聞いて！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Listen to what she's saying!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 78.9233571562,
      "endTime": 82.19911690079999,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "stm",
      "speakerName": "橋本さとみ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Satomi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-satomi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2303_01_05/sud_vo_adv_event_2303_01_05-stm005.m4a",
      "text": "鍛え抜かれたプロとしてのみなさんは、当然ステキです\nでも、それはもう見せてもらっているんです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "As professionals who have been trained‚ of course‚ you're all wonderful.\nBut you've already shown that.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 82.3900238228,
      "endTime": 89.6063970756,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "stm",
      "speakerName": "橋本さとみ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Satomi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-satomi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2303_01_05/sud_vo_adv_event_2303_01_05-stm006.m4a",
      "text": "そしてこの合宿を通じて、私、気付いたんです\n普段のみなさんにも、それに負けない魅力があるって",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Through this training camp‚ I realized something.\nThere's charm in each of you‚ even beyond your usual selves.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 89.8063970995,
      "endTime": 98.5990738344,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "stm",
      "speakerName": "橋本さとみ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Satomi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-satomi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2303_01_05/sud_vo_adv_event_2303_01_05-stm007.m4a",
      "text": "だからあえて逆に！　プロのアイドルではなく\n素の魅力を強調したユニットにしたいんです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "So I dare say! Instead of professional idols‚\nI want to emphasize the charm of your true selves in this unit.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 98.7990738582,
      "endTime": 105.56880280489999,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2303_01_05/sud_vo_adv_event_2303_01_05-szk002.m4a",
      "text": "……確かに……今までにない、新しいコンセプト……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…Certainly… a new concept we haven't seen before…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 105.7688028287,
      "endTime": 110.85483455170001,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "stm",
      "speakerName": "橋本さとみ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Satomi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-satomi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2303_01_05/sud_vo_adv_event_2303_01_05-stm008.m4a",
      "text": "合宿のお陰でアイデアもどんどんわいてきてます\nでもそれは――ここにいる五人じゃないとダメなんです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Thanks to the training camp‚ ideas are bubbling up one after another.\nBu―― it has to be these five people here.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 111.0548345755,
      "endTime": 119.0866203498,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "stm",
      "speakerName": "橋本さとみ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Satomi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-satomi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2303_01_05/sud_vo_adv_event_2303_01_05-stm009.m4a",
      "text": "あの合宿で見せてくれたみなさんの姿こそが\nこのユニットのコアなんですから",
      "translations": {
        "en": "The figures you showed at that camp…\nThat's the core of this unit.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 119.2866203736,
      "endTime": 125.19638685700001,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2303_01_05/sud_vo_adv_event_2303_01_05-suz003.m4a",
      "text": "それでさとみさん？　このユニットの……\nセンターは？　もう決まっていますの？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "So‚ Satomi-san? Is the center of this unit…\nalready decided?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 125.3963868808,
      "endTime": 133.78634125690002,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "stm",
      "speakerName": "橋本さとみ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Satomi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-satomi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2303_01_05/sud_vo_adv_event_2303_01_05-stm010.m4a",
      "text": "はい。私が決めました。この人しかいない\nそう自信をもって言えます",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yes. I've decided. There's no one else but her.\nI can say that with confidence.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 133.9863412808,
      "endTime": 140.2039385745,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "stm",
      "speakerName": "橋本さとみ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Satomi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-satomi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2303_01_05/sud_vo_adv_event_2303_01_05-stm011.m4a",
      "text": "……奥山すみれさん。センターは、あなたです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…Okuyama Sumire-san. The center is you.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 140.4039385984,
      "endTime": 144.6543844888,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2303_01_05/sud_vo_adv_event_2303_01_05-smr003.m4a",
      "text": "え……私？　どうして……？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Huh… me? Why…?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 144.8543845126,
      "endTime": 148.7683981845,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "stm",
      "speakerName": "橋本さとみ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Satomi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-satomi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2303_01_05/sud_vo_adv_event_2303_01_05-stm012.m4a",
      "text": "それは奥山さんが、このユニットのコンセプトを\n最も体現したアイドルだからです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Because Okuyama-san‚\nyou embody the concept of this unit the most.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 148.9543845126,
      "endTime": 155.0265021274,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2303_01_05/sud_vo_adv_event_2303_01_05-chs002.m4a",
      "text": "ふふっ。確かにすみれちゃんは、この合宿で一番\nありのままの姿を見せてくれたかも",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Hehe. Sumire-chan did indeed show her true self\nthe most at this training camp.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 155.2265021512,
      "endTime": 162.53945018739998,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2303_01_05/sud_vo_adv_event_2303_01_05-smr004.m4a",
      "text": "そ、そうかな……？　自分じゃ分からないよ～",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Is that so…? I don't really know myself~",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 162.7265021512,
      "endTime": 167.795345802,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kokoro",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2303_01_05/sud_vo_adv_event_2303_01_05-kkr004.m4a",
      "text": "そうですか？　自分の欲望に忠実になったり\nカレーのことでムキになったり",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Is that right? Being true to your desires\nGetting worked up over curry",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 167.9931688179,
      "endTime": 174.7265022148,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2303_01_05/sud_vo_adv_event_2303_01_05-chs003.m4a",
      "text": "みんなをまとめようと頑張って\nでもうまくいかなくて落ち込んだり……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Trying your best to bring everyone together\nbut feeling down when things don't go well…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 174.9265022386,
      "endTime": 181.07654744270002,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
