      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_stagesleeves-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stagesleeves-00-noon",
      "startTime": 360.9858470383
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "stm",
      "speakerName": "橋本さとみ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Satomi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-satomi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2303_01_05/sud_vo_adv_event_2303_01_05-stm019.m4a",
      "text": "ど、どうしたんですか？\nむしろ私がお世話された方では！？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "W-what's wrong?\nIf anything‚ I should be the one grateful‚ right!?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 360.9858470383,
      "endTime": 365.9231651726,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_stagesleeves-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stagesleeves-00-noon",
      "startTime": 366.1231651964
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2303_01_05/sud_vo_adv_event_2303_01_05-smr012.m4a",
      "text": "今回のお仕事を通して、気付けたんです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Through this job‚ I realized something.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 366.1231651964,
      "endTime": 369.54150998020003,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_stagesleeves-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stagesleeves-00-noon",
      "startTime": 369.7564985298
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2303_01_05/sud_vo_adv_event_2303_01_05-smr013.m4a",
      "text": "トリエルにいる時の私は、いつも\n瑠依ちゃんや優ちゃんに助けてもらってばかりで……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "When I'm at TRINITYAiLE‚\nI'm always relying on Rui-chan and Yu-chan…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 369.7564985298,
      "endTime": 376.35326862560004,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_stagesleeves-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stagesleeves-00-noon",
      "startTime": 376.7565005644
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2303_01_05/sud_vo_adv_event_2303_01_05-smr014.m4a",
      "text": "だから私も瑠依ちゃん達みたいに、みんなのこと\n助けたり、リードしようと頑張ったんですけど",
      "translations": {
        "en": "So I tried my best to help everyone and\nlead like Rui-chan and the others…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 376.7565005644,
      "endTime": 384.1396752699,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2303_01_05/sud_vo_adv_event_2303_01_05-smr015.m4a",
      "text": "でもそんなの、簡単に出来る訳ないですよね\nだって、私は私で、瑠依ちゃんじゃないんだから",
      "translations": {
        "en": "But I realized it's not that easy.\nBecause I'm me‚ not Rui-chan.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 384.4564985299,
      "endTime": 393.38012619259996,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_stagesleeves-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stagesleeves-00-noon",
      "startTime": 393.5898318632
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2303_01_05/sud_vo_adv_event_2303_01_05-smr016.m4a",
      "text": "――だから私は、このままの私で、頑張ります",
      "translations": {
        "en": "――So I'll keep going as myself.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 393.5898318632,
      "endTime": 397.7977002485,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_stagesleeves-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stagesleeves-00-noon",
      "startTime": 397.9898318632
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2303_01_05/sud_vo_adv_event_2303_01_05-smr017.m4a",
      "text": "頑張り続けて、成長すれば、きっといつか\n瑠依ちゃんみたいになれるって、思うから",
      "translations": {
        "en": "If I keep trying and growing‚ I believe that someday…\nI can become like Rui-chan.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 397.9898318632,
      "endTime": 404.71019481260004,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_stagesleeves-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stagesleeves-00-noon",
      "startTime": 404.9231651965
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "stm",
      "speakerName": "橋本さとみ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Satomi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-satomi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2303_01_05/sud_vo_adv_event_2303_01_05-stm020.m4a",
      "text": "奥山さん……今すぐ抱き締めたい……！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Okuyama-san… I want to hug you right now…!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 404.9231651965,
      "endTime": 408.58877627280003,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_stagesleeves-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stagesleeves-00-noon",
      "startTime": 408.7887762966
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2303_01_05/sud_vo_adv_event_2303_01_05-suz012.m4a",
      "text": "盛り上がってるところ悪いですけど\nそろそろ本番ですわよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Sorry to interrupt the excitement‚ but\nit's time for the main event.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 408.7887762966,
      "endTime": 413.5922457638,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_stagesleeves-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stagesleeves-00-noon",
      "startTime": 413.7922457876
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2303_01_05/sud_vo_adv_event_2303_01_05-smr018.m4a",
      "text": "じゃあみんな、輪になろう！　さとみさんも一緒に！\n六人目のメンバーなんですから！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Then‚ everyone‚ let's form a circle! Satomi-san too!\nYou're the sixth member!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 413.7922457876,
      "endTime": 420.21351549049996,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_stagesleeves-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stagesleeves-00-noon",
      "startTime": 417.9947710351
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "stm",
      "speakerName": "橋本さとみ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Satomi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-satomi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2303_01_05/sud_vo_adv_event_2303_01_05-stm022.m4a",
      "text": "わ、私もですか！？\nありがとうございます、では失礼して……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "M-me too!?\nThank you‚ then I'll excuse myself…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 420.425579121,
      "endTime": 426.3646582149,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
